efill your heart!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197550/extras/c00015e9edad1e174ad154f93efb2a03.poster.avif?t=1762514464\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197550/extras/c00015e9edad1e174ad154f93efb2a03.webm?t=1762514464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197550/extras/c00015e9edad1e174ad154f93efb2a03.mp4?t=1762514464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When things get too difficult, you can always rely on Starkat to cheer you up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the line blurs between Starkat and the real world, many surprises await you in this epic quest for love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may laugh, you may cry, you will almost definitely be frustrated.</p>",
